Alpha 0.1.0

The Release

For the first release, a ton has been added since the Prototype version :

- New World Generation using Seeds (including 4 new type of biomes!)
- Over 15 new blocks you can use.
- A functional hotbar with the ability to pick up blocks when destroyed.
- An infinite world!
- 9 new ores (including 2 custom ones such as ruby and titanium!)
- Water, lakes and rivers!
- FPS and Coordinates UI!
- A whole Menu Screen!
- A launcher for the game! (Made by Avery)

We are planning on releasing tons of new stuff for Alpha 0.1.1! Though we'll need some time to implement them :)
